OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Twitch has apologised, after a backlash
OL,6, over new advertising rules.            
OL,8,FThe Amazon-owned livestreaming service 
OL,9,Fhad said it would restrict the size and
OL,10,Ftype of ads used by streamers who      
OL,11,Fcreate content on Twitch.              
OL,13,FThis would have substantially reduced  
OL,14,Fthe ways in which streamers generate   
OL,15,Fincome on the platform.                
OL,17,FTwitch has now said it will rewrite the
OL,18,Fnew policy, after several prominent    
OL,19,Fcreators threatened to boycott the     
OL,20,Fplatform - and some moved elsewhere.   
